# Everything the image should not carry. Keeps the build context small and
# ensures deps are resolved fresh from the lockfile inside the image.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.turbo
.turbo
**/.next
**/coverage

# Never bake env files / secrets into the image (Fly injects env + secrets).
**/.env
**/.env.*

.git
.gitignore
**/*.log
.planning
.agents
**/.DS_Store
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
